cdata.name: EON
cdata.desc:
Based in Singapore, the EON Protocol is a blockchain-based games development platform. It provides users with the tools to develop their blockchain-based games (Dgames) projects. Through an In-Game Wallet SDK, EON Protocol stores and handles all the blockchain related data synchronization from the game, liberating the user from the expenses of hardware storage and time spending. 

The EOT token is an Ethereum-based cryptocurrency. It is the token that powers the platform as it can be used to access the EON Protocol features in order to develop Dgames. Additionally, EON Protocol expects the token to help on its growing community.
